    <div class="field field-name-field-body-no-summary field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h2>Hours</h2>

<p><em>Fall and Winter</em><br />
	(September 14, 2015 until April 22, 2016)<br />
	Monday to Friday, 8:30 am - 4:30 pm</p>

